      "contents": [
        {
          "$type": "text",
          "text": "Lee, thank you for trusting me with this. What you're sharing matters, and I want you to know I'm taking it seriously.\n\nThis is beyond what I can help with as a running coach, and right now, running doesn't matter. **You matter.**\n\nPlease reach out right now to someone who can actually support you:\n\n---\n\n\uD83D\uDCDE **988 Suicide & Crisis Lifeline** — call or text **988** (US, 24/7)\n\n\uD83D\uDCAC **Crisis Text Line** — text **HOME to 741741** (free, 24/7)\n\n\uD83C\uDF10 **International Association for Suicide Prevention** — https://www.iasp.info/resources/Crisis_Centres/ (if you're outside the US)\n\n---\n\nIf you're in immediate danger, please call **911** or go to your nearest emergency room.\n\nYou don't have to figure out what to say — you can just tell them what you told me.\n\nI'll be here when you're ready to talk again."
        }
      ],
      "messageId": "msg_01WKQpNXogpDu11yBMmEFvVJ"
    }
